<br>
I get into a BOT group, run to hub, pull random_mob_01, FD, get up and attack from behind (smack/smack/kick/kick), &quot;you get experience&quot;, rinse repeat.  Occasionally a spec drops but monks don't get those.  Occasionally a named spawns and then dies using the same pattern and once a month when the stars align it will be both a monk item (leather pattern) and the RNG makes me the winner. <br>
