<br>
Corpse runs used to be very thrilling, very exciting.  Everyone I know hated it, particularly if you died someplace where the zone in wasn't safe (Fear anyone?).  And losing exp every time you died, now that made the game challenging.  Death had a real meaning.  Die deep in a dungeon, and there was a real chance that you might not get your stuff back.  I remember dying once in Befallen, and wondering if I was ever going to be able to find and loot that banded armor I had taken so long to get.    <br>
<br>
Then we all levelled up.  Guilds got bigger and stronger.  Clerics got rezz.  Necros and SKs got summon corpse, and necros got rezz too.  Suddenly, it didn't matter if you died, or where you died.  You'd just get a guildie to come summon your corpse, and another one to rezz you.  Die in Fear, and there was always someone to drag you to a safe spot for a rezz, or a friendly guild to break the zone in for you.  <br>
<br>
The game was a heck of a lot more thrilling and exciting when death had a real consequence.  Unfortunately, that was the thing people complained about the most.  There's a reason why there are graveyards in PoP, and it's because the customers demanded them.  So, if we think the game isn't as thrilling as it used to be, we have no one to blame but ourselves. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showMessageRange?topicID=3544.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showMessageRange?topicID=3544.topic&start=41&stop=59>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showPrevMessage?topicID=3544.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showNextMessage?topicID=3544.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3544.topic&index=40><img src=http://members.cox.net/cbilyeu/tavern/notnice_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.emailToFriend?topicID=3544.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.threadControl?topicID=3544.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3544.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive